---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Joseph Rowe's First Astro Blog</h1>
			<p>
				If you've somehow found this page while I'm still developing it, congrats. Keep up the good work.
				<br/>
				<br/>
				My name is Joseph Rowe. I'm a content strategist, editorial lead, and occasional writer at Codeless.
				<br/>
				<br/>
				Check me out on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/josephrowe/">LinkedIn</a> and <a href="https://github.com/Yosef73">GitHub</a>.
				<br/>
				<br/>
				I've created this site to serve as a fun side project and to experiment with some of my more technical/development related interests.
				<br/>
				<br/>
				I've created this site with Astro. Not sure if I'll add anything beyond the basics for now.
				<br/>
				<br/>
				Toodles.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
